♪ Find who we are

38:06.836 --> 38:08.872
♪ Find who we are

38:08.907 --> 38:11.323
♪ Find who we are

38:11.358 --> 38:13.152
♪ Find who we are

38:13.187 --> 38:15.223
♪ Find who we are

38:15.258 --> 38:16.155
♪ Find who we are

38:16.190 --> 38:18.503
♪ It takes time

38:19.331 --> 38:21.195
I didn't get married.

38:23.024 --> 38:24.647
You didn't get married.

38:28.513 --> 38:29.652
[ Gasps ]

38:29.686 --> 38:31.309
You two should go.

38:32.482 --> 38:33.552
Yeah, yeah.

38:33.587 --> 38:35.036
I'll be fine.

38:35.071 --> 38:37.763
♪ It's like lightning

38:38.833 --> 38:41.457
♪ When it strikes,
then you know ♪

38:41.491 --> 38:43.044
...what you believe
the sign means...

38:43.079 --> 38:44.460
♪ It's the right thing

38:44.494 --> 38:47.255
♪ Am I on my own?

38:47.290 --> 38:49.499
...what you believe
you deserve.

38:50.604 --> 38:53.123
♪ Walking blindly

38:54.504 --> 38:58.163
♪ But I'm searching for,
try to follow the stars ♪

38:58.197 --> 39:00.959
♪ But don't know
where they are ♪

39:01.925 --> 39:04.445
♪ Give me the secret

39:05.412 --> 39:09.485
♪ Don't hold out about it

39:09.519 --> 39:12.350
♪ Started to see it

39:16.146 --> 39:20.219
♪ Sometimes
it's heaven or hell ♪

39:20.254 --> 39:24.051
♪ It's getting harder to tell

39:24.085 --> 39:28.331
♪ But I think
I'm finding myself ♪

39:31.990 --> 39:36.063
♪ I might be going nowhere

39:36.097 --> 39:38.306
♪ Nowhere

39:39.480 --> 39:43.726
♪ But I know
I'm gonna get there ♪

39:43.760 --> 39:47.074
♪ I know I'm gonna get there

39:47.108 --> 39:49.317
♪ It reminds me

39:49.352 --> 39:54.461
♪ That nothing is ever
what it seems ♪

39:54.495 --> 39:57.947
♪ Give me the secret

39:57.981 --> 40:02.158
♪ Don't hold out about it

40:02.192 --> 40:05.610
♪ Started to see it

40:05.644 --> 40:09.614
♪ Even though it's clouded

40:09.648 --> 40:15.654
♪♪

40:16.759 --> 40:20.556
